sh <scriptname.sh> - to run Shell files

crontab - scheduler
eg: crontab -e -> to open cron tab editor and  * * * * * echo "Hello world from crontab"

crontab - l -> to list output
* * * * * ->  min hour day month weekday(0-6)

sudo tail -f /var/log/cron - to check crontab logs


eg: crontab -e -> to open cron tab editor and  * * * * * sh /home/ec2-user/shell-practice/5_Shell.sh
sudo tail -f /var/log/cron - to check crontab logs of that script